  "logNo": "220292117372",
  "title": "행복이넘치는하루",
  "addDate": "2015. 3. 6.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220292117372",
  "html_size": 186903,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220292117372\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220292117372\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">안녕하세요^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오래간만에 글올려요&nbsp;ㅎㅎ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘은 우리 김샘 생신이라&nbsp;아침에는 원장님께서 케잌을 들고오셨어요 ㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">짜잔~</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a8261145333032f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"319\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 319px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20150306_213/isuhani_1425622854159edqoM_JPEG/DSC03685.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a8261145333032f.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">(생일축하 노래부르고 바로 케잌잘라서 폭풍흡입하느라 사진을 못찍어가지구</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">사진은 인터넷에서 구했어요 ㅠㅠ)</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">초코 쉬폰 케잌인데요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">너무너무 맛있어요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/moon_and_james/original/64.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-64\"></a></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/full/20130612/emoticon/3_48.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/full\\/20130612\\/emoticon\\/3_48.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/full/20130612/emoticon/3_48.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\">생일축하합니다 생일축하합니다 사랑하는 우리김샘~ 생일축하합니다~<img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/full/20130612/emoticon/4_13.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/full\\/20130612\\/emoticon\\/4_13.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/full/20130612/emoticon/4_13.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">짝짝~ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">원장님 센스만점이세요 ㅋㅋ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">개인적으로 제가 초코케잌 좋아하거든요 ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/moon_and_james/original/2.png\" width=\"105\" height=\"120\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 105px; height: 120px;\" alt=\"moon_and_james-2\"></a></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래서 더 맛있었나봐요 히힛</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그리고 오전 진료중에 환자분께서 빵이랑 에그타르트를 사다주셨는데요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_52/isuhani_1425623258227iFt26_JPEG/P3064073.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20150306_52/isuhani_1425623258227iFt26_JPEG/P3064073.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_52/isuhani_1425623258227iFt26_JPEG/P3064073.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">전에&nbsp;제가 말한 그 '에그타르트는 사랑입니다'했던 그 에그타르트에요 ㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c0bb8ab0bf482e83.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20150306_187/isuhani_1425623258603kWBSv_JPEG/P3064078.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c0bb8ab0bf482e83.jpg\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">타르트 안에있는 에그가 보들보들 말캉말캉 ㅋㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">완전 맛있어요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">진짜 먹어도 먹어도 안질리는 보떼엠 에그타르트는 <img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/full/20130612/emoticon/1_24.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/full\\/20130612\\/emoticon\\/1_24.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/full/20130612/emoticon/1_24.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\">&nbsp;ㅋㅋㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">같이 주신 다른빵은.. 뭐지.. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_38/isuhani_1425623258464VRgpD_JPEG/P3064075.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"299\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 299px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20150306_38/isuhani_1425623258464VRgpD_JPEG/P3064075.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_38/isuhani_1425623258464VRgpD_JPEG/P3064075.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">뭔가 건강하게 생겼죠? ㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">호두도 있구 잣도있구 씨앗도있구 베리도있구 겉에는 보리같은게 붙어있는데..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이것도 너무 맛있어요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오후에는 매일 오시는 다른 환자분깨서 원장님이 좋아하신다고 가래떡도 사다주셨어요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘따라 환자분들께서 많이 많이 챙겨주시네요 ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘 김샘 생신인거 다들 아시는건가? ㅋㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_124/isuhani_1425623258855fsis9_JPEG/P3064084.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20150306_124/isuhani_1425623258855fsis9_JPEG/P3064084.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000334A6EF37C')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20150306_124/isuhani_1425623258855fsis9_JPEG/P3064084.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘 하루는 행복이 넘치는 하루인거같아요 ㅋㅋ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">우리 원장님이랑 선생님들이랑 환자분들도 모두 웃는모습이 보기 좋네요 ㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">매일매일이 오늘같았으면 좋겠어요.. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">매일매일 행복한하루, 웃음이 넘치는 하루.. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">김샘, 다시한번 생신 축하드려요 ^^ 항상 건강하시고 행복하세요 ^^ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/line_characters_in_love/original/1.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-1\"></a></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
